data.eml:eml: Sakakibarana, a new genus of Gyponini (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Iassinae) from the Amazon Rainforest

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Gonçalves, Clayton Corrêa, Takiya, Daniela Maeda, Mejdalani, Gabriel (2017): Sakakibarana, a new genus of Gyponini (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Iassinae) from the Amazon Rainforest. Zootaxa 4281 (1): 219-224, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4281.1.20
